{"tid":2236239,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"譚朗蔚話阿里巴巴唔會急跌","createTime":"2020-10-09T10:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T10:32:51.000Z","uid":233098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3de961ddd01ef9cce75f211340397bc49e528d07","tid":2236239,"uid":233098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:26:20.000Z","msg":"本來預料由28名港交所專家組成的小組，於上周舉行上市聆訊，最快九月底披露招股說明書，並於10月中下旬正式完成「A+H」同步上市，但至今尚未成事。有消息指，昨日（8日）的上市委員會例會，螞蟻仍未聆訊。受到消息影響，阿里股價今午由紀錄高位293元倒跌1.5%，收市報285.2元，跌3元。<br />\n<br />\n富昌證券聯席董事譚朗蔚，認為投資者無須過分擔心，他認為近來阿里股價造好，並非單靠市場憧憬上市因素支撐。雖然短期內未必成功維持破頂位置，但不會因上市出現變數而急跌，有273、 258兩個支持位，「佢下方啱啱喺過去一個月，有幾好嘅支持，亦突破上嚟，所以唔應該估佢短線會急跌幾多。」<br />\n<br />\n呢排佢燈到咁，各位要睇路了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_762353_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_762353_0&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYznd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=93a70132\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_762353_0&h=4fd164fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_762353_0</a>"},{"pid":"70a43a430678604230d79ea9c42589a6c72d1e09","tid":2236239,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://0007.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0007.HK&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYznd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=c3e71c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0007.HK</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}